    <stitle>SPICER 14 INCH (350 MM) SOLO CLUTCH - LUBRICATION - RELEASE BEARING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>RELEASE BEARING</title>
        <para>The release bearing housing has been pre-packed with grease, however, the release bearing should be
            lubricated at each chassis lubrication, and at regular maintenance intervals with a recommended lubricant.
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Apply grease to the transmission shaft to lube the bushing inside the release bearing sleeve
                    assembly.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
